libintl-perl: libintl-perl (Internationalization for Perl)
libintl-perl:
libintl-perl: libintl-perl is a library that supports message translation for Perl,
libintl-perl: written in pure Perl (version 5.004 or better). Its interface is very 
libintl-perl: similar to the gettext family of functions in C, and it uses the same 
libintl-perl: file formats as GNU gettext, making it possible to use all tools 
libintl-perl: available for gettext itself and to seamlessly integrate 
libintl-perl: internationalized Perl code into mixed-language projects.
